<br>
Players come from far more than English speaking countries so in fairness names would have to be policed to make them suitable for every language. How would Akylah feel if she was told she had to change the name of the char she had invested so much time in because her name was surprisingly close to the Czech/Arab/Zambian word for smegma?<br>
